module.exports = divide

/**
 * Divides two vec2's
 *
 * @param {vec2} out the receiving vector
 * @param {vec2} a the first operand
 * @param {vec2} b the second operand
 * @returns {vec2} out
 */
function divide(out, a, b) {
    out[0] = a[0] / b[0]
    out[1] = a[1] / b[1]
    return out
}
